- Top note.

465
00:22:14,791 --> 00:22:16,376
And this is a heart note.

466
00:22:16,877 --> 00:22:18,962
- This is a base note.
- Base note.

467
00:22:19,046 --> 00:22:23,342
The top note of your perfume
is the part that you will smell first.

468
00:22:23,425 --> 00:22:27,137
